Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.52,0:00:05.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是近江神宮…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.61,0:00:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歌留多的聖地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.32,0:00:09.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參拜的禮節是鞠躬兩次 拍手兩次 再鞠躬一次
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.91,0:00:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們可能會覺得這些規矩形式什麼的很麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但神明的心胸不一定是寬廣的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.29,0:00:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謹守禮儀 許下你們的願望吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.13,0:00:31.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不奢望奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.14,0:00:39.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請保佑大家不要發生意外
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保佑大家發揮出練習時的水平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.27,0:00:53.03,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}比賽場地是在其他地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:55.82,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是的 在旁邊那座叫「勸學館」的楼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 走啦 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.28,0:00:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:01:00.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒好像有個全部參賽者集合起來參拜的儀式
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.08,0:01:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊? 所有人又要一起來這兒?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.29,0:01:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於來到這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.42,0:01:07.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,近江神宮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.79,0:01:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的夢想…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.80,0:01:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然一如往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.30,0:01:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那綾瀨同學就是女王了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.06,0:02:53.11,title_text,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur11\fad(864,811)\pos(490,301)}初春入田野
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.48,0:02:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱——
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個好熱啊 小奏
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.24,0:03:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要穿袴了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次的全國大會 就讓我們正裝上陣吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.07,0:03:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會場裡好像是有空調的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奏!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.20,0:03:10.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真島的衣服交給媽媽我來幫他穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那千早的衣服呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是已經穿好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.43,0:03:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她不動也不說話 所以看起來還像是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.23,0:03:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯? 才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.52,0:03:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.40,0:03:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是在E組啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.48,0:03:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 裡邊沒有超強的隊伍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:42.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.61,0:03:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據瘦子的資料所言
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.28,0:03:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要注意的是靜岡的富士崎高中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.66,0:03:49.16,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是哪個? 是哪些人?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本地的善德寺高中…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.45,0:03:50.75,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}我看看我看看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.70,0:03:51.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代表福井的國彌高中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.87,0:03:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年在預賽贏了北央
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷新…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.96,0:04:01.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有報名參加明天的個人賽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的就是東京代表隊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 據說他們贏了北央學园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擊敗北央的須藤的人是哪個?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧 須藤輸了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.98,0:04:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們社團真的才組建了3個月嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有多強啊
Comment: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:29.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{畫面注}佐賀縣代表 武知高校 特點: 歌留多部建立8年,去年打入全國賽,也進入淘汰賽,在第一輪被淘汰.其他時候沒有過更好的成績.需要注意的是B級的井上龍平和田中彩子二人.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們首戰的對手 是佐賀的武知高中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很…很強嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.91,0:04:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們很強嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.04,0:04:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是有兩人是B級 其他人沒有段位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的順序怎麼排?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按照對陣北央時一樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.25,0:04:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有道理 那是最好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我當棄子就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:46.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我和最強的家伙對戰!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼呢 那怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.64,0:04:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:51.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使我輸了 剩下四人贏了就行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.06,0:04:54.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能提高獲勝概率的話 我什麼都肯做
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.77,0:04:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要晋級!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.19,0:04:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是東京代表啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.82,0:05:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,書桌小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得分能手大多會排在兩端和正中
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:07.57,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.87,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}那駒野在最前 接著是大江同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.99,0:05:10.53,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}是!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.41,0:05:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為有大家在…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.87,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑞!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.29,0:05:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澤!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.79,0:05:14.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.29,0:05:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.87,0:05:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:18.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要晋級!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家齊心協力!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.38,0:05:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜錯了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.97,0:05:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 請大家擺好牌
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.24,0:05:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:53.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:03.42,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}なにわずに　さくやこのはな　ふゆごもり
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.33,0:06:03.42,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「花映難波津 隆冬且暫隱」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:12.01,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.59,0:06:12.01,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又將至 再綻此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好多帥氣的孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記錄記錄
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些孩子實力有多強呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:24.15,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}いまをはるべと　さくやこのはな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.85,0:06:24.15,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「初春又將至 再綻此花矣」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:20.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真是的 連我都緊張起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.32,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,あけぬれば…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.28,0:06:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「冬曉催人散…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.32,0:06:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很僵硬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.41,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,6)}たきのおとは…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.41,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(640,48)}「飛練餘枯影…」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:35.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點放鬆下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.33,0:06:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要盡快!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.54,0:06:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諸位!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一張一張地搶到手吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:54.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.68,0:06:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袴好熱啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.27,0:06:59.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聲音好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.60,0:07:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人太多了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吵…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.73,0:07:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.48,0:07:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對 好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.61,0:07:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神明啊 為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是向您祈求過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.74,0:07:16.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說過「請保佑大家不要發生意外」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我并不奢求奇迹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.55,0:07:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走錯路了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明來過幾次了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.55,0:07:35.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為每次都是坐車來的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.65,0:07:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,癱瘓?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:50.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是身體右邊部分變得比較難以活動了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.07,0:07:52.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 你可能會被嚇到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.78,0:07:56.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼? 爺爺就是爺爺啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.79,0:08:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子他爺爺 新來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.88,0:08:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 新…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.09,0:08:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是爺爺啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.68,0:08:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 我給你做了全新的擺法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快拿紙記下來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牌都要亂掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.32,0:08:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺不會認輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正努力只用左手也能搶牌
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.29,0:08:41.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在滋賀縣的近江神宮
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我們也送上現場直播
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.75,0:08:49.04,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}挑戰三連霸的名人三木先生的 是周防久志選手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺啊 名人戰是什麼樣的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.13,0:08:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}周防選手是在校的大學生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.38,0:08:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺也會緊張嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.26,0:08:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全不會
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.47,0:08:57.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過會在比賽前讓我擺好造型拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.22,0:09:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微有點成了明星的感覺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.73,0:09:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 去想像一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.15,0:09:09.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想象自己正身處那個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燈光很亮很熱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許許多多人看著你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼前是最強的名人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.91,0:09:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能聽見拍打榻榻米的聲音的近江勸學館
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想像一下吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.12,0:09:28.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會獲勝的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快點回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:47.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺在等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說是輕微的發作
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為爺爺的心臟比較弱
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醫生說觀察一下 明天就可以回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:09.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.29,0:10:12.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 嚇我一跳啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還坐上了救護車…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:19.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是哪位啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.85,0:10:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,腦部發現萎縮了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.31,0:10:25.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是早期的痴呆症狀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.14,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 這個是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.78,0:10:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.66,0:10:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.91,0:10:45.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.67,0:10:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.55,0:10:58.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.68,0:11:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.59,0:11:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:06.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新! 新!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說翔二在昨天的大會拿了冠軍 升到A級了!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.44,0:11:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我原以為最先拿到的絕對應該是你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:17.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過你比賽和練習都沒有參加…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.15,0:11:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是沒辦法的…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綿谷!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.49,0:11:20.95,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}翔二 我說你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.11,0:11:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然以前你的名人爺爺讓你很自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.53,0:11:23.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過現在可是反過來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.45,0:11:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你應該覺得要是沒有他 就有時間練習了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好快!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.74,0:11:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 老師!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:29.83,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}上啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「升上C級了」…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.55,0:11:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也在好好努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.26,0:11:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然信裡說自己加入了田徑部
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.47,0:11:44.47,writings1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz17.921\a5\move(408,384,408,454)}新也一定在努力吧 \N我們有機會再比試吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.14,0:11:50.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這週星期天中午 我有個同學聚會
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.48,0:11:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能請你照顧爺爺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.52,0:11:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:54.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會盡早回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.11,0:11:59.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽頭髮白了不少啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來去不成了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.78,0:12:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.33,0:12:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險的 會灑出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.04,0:12:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先放下來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.63,0:12:21.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袴…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.51,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把袴拿出來!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須得去福井大會!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 今年你不用去參加啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.27,0:12:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不去?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:36.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 恢復以前的樣子了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.52,0:12:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼「但是」!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.98,0:12:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能把大會丟在一邊 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.99,0:12:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是爺爺他…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 爸爸中午過後就會回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.67,0:12:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.00,0:12:59.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想落在大家後面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:02.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想早點升上A級!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.26,0:13:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.59,0:13:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去想像一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.39,0:13:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.86,0:13:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.62,0:13:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.72,0:13:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好辛苦…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耳鳴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像要倒下了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.76,0:14:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻…要進攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.81,0:14:41.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣結束!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.86,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請等一下!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨棄權
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.91,0:14:57.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 請讓一讓
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.79,0:14:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 借過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.12,0:15:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.63,0:15:03.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.13,0:15:06.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太一 千早怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.72,0:15:13.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.85,0:15:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有四個人 我們也會贏的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.19,0:15:21.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨同學!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.90,0:15:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是綾瀨同學的朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.90,0:15:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.02,0:15:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶她去等候室 快點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.99,0:15:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.37,0:15:37.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:39.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.46,0:15:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要進攻…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.54,0:15:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能就這樣結束的!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.15,0:16:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還有比賽…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.28,0:16:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不去不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.15,0:16:11.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 你得躺著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.15,0:16:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比賽已經棄權了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.87,0:16:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,棄權…?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 都說不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你老實呆著
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.54,0:16:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.83,0:16:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去了也沒用 你已經不能重回比賽了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.92,0:16:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幹 我不幹!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.38,0:16:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明努力過了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家約好了…要贏下來的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.12,0:16:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.74,0:17:01.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是跟以前一樣的直率
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.46,0:17:06.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在思考著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.04,0:17:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於歌留多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:14.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於歌留多和…爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.90,0:17:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要去市民醫院的急诊室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.31,0:17:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會告訴真島同學他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個女孩在比賽中好像就一直身體不適
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望沒什麼大礙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你不是綿谷嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.91,0:17:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是聯盟的…吉岡老師
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.79,0:17:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你還記得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直很担心你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.84,0:17:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從去年開始你就沒有參加過任何大會了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這個大會你參加了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:17:59.47,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}不 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:17:59.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真令人期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能再見到綿谷老師了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.18,0:18:10.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你的歌留多 和綿谷老師一模一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 比賽也差不多要結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:15.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼下次見
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.38,0:18:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.21,0:18:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很喜歡…歌留多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.48,0:18:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太離譜了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.28,0:18:59.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太離譜了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.45,0:19:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 為什麼北央的人會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我報名參加了明天的個人戰啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.54,0:19:13.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說 因身體不適而棄權算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是以東京代表的身份出賽的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 你以為哭就能得到原諒嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.13,0:19:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被別人以為東京的實力很弱的話怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.64,0:19:25.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:28.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千早 不用躺著休息嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.94,0:19:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對…對不起 各位…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.77,0:19:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…你這是做什麼呢 千早
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼好道歉的啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.53,0:19:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,綾瀨 我今天第一次獲勝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.45,0:19:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 而且還是二連勝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和對方都還剩七張的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我猜中了 搶到了「秋色」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.83,0:19:50.87,waka,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(785,658)}しら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.08,0:19:53.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那一張决定了勝負吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然在复賽的淘汰賽中輸給了富士崎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過好想再賽幾場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身體狀態不能马上恢复吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.30,0:20:04.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭明早第一班新幹線回去如何
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到現在還按捺不住興奮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.64,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對要恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以完美的身體狀態迎戰明天的個人賽!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.65,0:20:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事 好多了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.19,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天能出場嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.57,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…今天我真的是很沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是…讓新失望了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難得他來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.12,0:20:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想讓他看看我出色的表現呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.08,0:20:36.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且你好重
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:39.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎? 不會吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本來以為會很輕 結果重得要命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.85,0:20:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新拜托負責管理的吉岡老師轉交給我們的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.60,0:20:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是福井的特產
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:03.37,note,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fad(400,0)\fn楷体\shad0\bord0\c&H65757D&}下次在比賽中見 新
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.03,0:21:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達到了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的心意…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.17,0:21:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給新了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
